              "free_text": [
                "The thicknesses of the Cd",
                " layers were 21.9 um in average.",
                " The stacks containing eight cadmium layers",
                " electrodeposited on copper backing and three 10.9 um",
                " thick Ti foils for monitoring the beam. Bombarding",
                " energy was 51.2 MeV determined by Time of Flight",
                " method. irradiation time was 2 h with an average beam",
                " current of Ia = 50 nA."
